rComments: Desiree Yomtoob was my substitue TA for a day for ENG 267 and she was phenomenal!! She is very intelligent, passionate, and very genuine and those are some very RARE qualities. I had only one class session with her but she had made a huge impact and impression on me and what she taught just really resonated with me. You will learn so much from her!
Hilariously strange. An okay teacher but goes off on tangents too often. Usually seems under the influence of something.
